Package: VariantPackage
Title: S4 Classes for Genetic Variant annotation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Martina", "Montonati", , "martina.montonati@studenti.unimi.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R package that provides a set of S4 classes for representing different genetic variants. It includes validating variant data, accessing variant attributes, and visualizing variant information.
